{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-docs-tsx","path":"/0.7/docs/editor-component-spine-cn","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>spine 组件用于给实体添加 spine 动画效果。</p>\n<h3 id=\"组件添加\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0\" aria-label=\"组件添加 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>组件添加</h3>\n<p>在<a href=\"/0.7/docs/editor-hierarchy-cn\">节点树</a>中，创建并点击选中实体（Entity）。</p>\n<p> <img src=\"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/OasisHub/4db9a2d5-9a37-4a27-b2a1-0aafb30ad5cd/1626681634222-8beabf17-8f7f-43de-8310-d18e32e27eac.png\" alt=\"img\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" /> </p>\n<p>在<a href=\"/0.7/docs/editor-inspector-cn\">检查器面板</a>中，点击添加组件按钮，选择 spine 动画。</p>\n<p> <img src=\"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/OasisHub/08c20b89-7df9-4d7d-a961-86e6382e7657/1626750041954-834ddb16-f66e-4f7b-b2b5-112f580e3714.png\" alt=\"img\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" /> </p>\n<p>添加完毕后，能够在<a href=\"/0.7/docs/editor-inspector-cn\">检查器面板</a>中看到 spine 组件：</p>\n<p> <img src=\"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/OasisHub/f63e85bf-2f1f-42a7-bd60-f03db615785b/1626682071627-aa55a319-fd35-44b4-adae-98fcababca86.png\" alt=\"img\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" /> </p>\n<h3 id=\"组件使用\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\" aria-label=\"组件使用 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>组件使用</h3>\n<h4 id=\"资产选择\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%B5%84%E4%BA%A7%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9\" aria-label=\"资产选择 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>资产选择</h4>\n<p>点击组件的 resource 选项，进入资产选择模式，选择资产面板中的 <a href=\"/0.7/docs/editor-resource-spine-cn\">spine 资产</a>。</p>\n<p> <img src=\"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/OasisHub/3177ad2d-d4a2-4390-95b9-0b11dc142f70/1626750237947-f457782d-807c-4a04-87fa-10f99dbb1a0b.png\" alt=\"img\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" /> </p>\n<p>选中后，就能够在预览窗口中看到 spine 动画了。</p>\n<p> <img src=\"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/OasisHub/6b7cb0dd-6a23-448d-8f8c-17ff3978e06d/1626682342975-ec2ac65d-9b72-48ce-9803-0ea27c061c69.png\" alt=\"img\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" /> </p>\n<h4 id=\"参数调整\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4\" aria-label=\"参数调整 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>参数调整</h4>\n<p>资产选择完毕后，可以通过调整组件参数实现以下效果：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>动画选择：点击 <code>animationName</code> 按钮，能够下拉选择需要播放的动画</li>\n<li>自动播放：选中 <code>autoPlay</code> 能够让动画自动播放</li>\n<li>缩放调整：调整 <code>scale</code> 的数值能够修改 spine 动画的缩放，改变其大小</li>\n</ul>\n<p> <img src=\"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/OasisHub/db05bb60-79a9-486d-bec5-2e5519d047b8/1626682566952-675311f9-5cb0-4bc1-86fa-2717ac9e23cc.png\" alt=\"img\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" /> </p>\n<h4 id=\"脚本控制\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6\" aria-label=\"脚本控制 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>脚本控制</h4>\n<p>如果 spine 组件本身提供组件参数不能满足开发的需要，我们能够借助<a href=\"/0.7/docs/editor-component-script-cn\">脚本组件</a>实现更加复杂的控制。</p>\n<p>如下图所示，在脚本的 <code>onAwake</code> 生命周期中，能够通过<a href=\"/0.7/docs/editor-script-communication-cn\">事件系统</a>对外暴露 spine 动画播放事件。</p>\n<p>当事件触发时，会执行回调函数 <code>playAnimation</code>（左侧事件通信测试面板能手动触发事件）。</p>\n<p>在 <code>playAnimation</code> 函数中，通过 <code>getComponentsIncludeChildren</code> 方法，获取到了该实体中所有添加的 <code>SpineAnimation</code> 组件。</p>\n<p>我们获取第一个 <code>SpineAnimation</code> 组件，通过其暴露的 <code>state</code> 对象播放动画。</p>\n<p><code>state</code> 对象是 spine 运行时的原生动画类。借助 <a href=\"http://zh.esotericsoftware.com/spine-api-reference#AnimationState\">AnimationState API</a> 以及 事件系统，就能实现更加复杂的动画控制了。</p>\n<p> <img src=\"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/OasisHub/410b495b-8078-4357-857f-5cec6f51dcf0/1626751647820-7681d1b3-1f36-45eb-9fbd-0516b6c2612f.png\" alt=\"img\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" /> </p>","htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"spine 组件用于给实体添加 spine 动画效果。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{"id":"组件添加","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0","ariaLabel":"组件添加 permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"组件添加"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在"},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"/0.7/docs/editor-hierarchy-cn"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"节点树"}]},{"type":"text","value":"中，创建并点击选中实体（Entity）。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":" "},{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/OasisHub/4db9a2d5-9a37-4a27-b2a1-0aafb30ad5cd/1626681634222-8beabf17-8f7f-43de-8310-d18e32e27eac.png","alt":"img","style":"zoom:50%;"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":" "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在"},{"type